                                            <label opaque="NO" userInteractionEnabled="NO" contentMode="left" horizontalHuggingPriority="251" verticalHuggingPriority="251" lineBreakMode="tailTruncation" numberOfLines="0" baselineAdjustment="alignBaselines" adjustsFontSizeToFit="NO" translatesAutoresizingMaskIntoConstraints="NO" id="1JU-Gx-3MV">
                                                <rect key="frame" x="15" y="321" width="345" height="244.5"/>
                                                <string key="text">Imaginglink collects personal information about health care 
professionals and others who may register to use the Site. 
Such information may include, without limitation, your name, 
email, physical address, phone and fax numbers, and, as 
applicable, details about medical training, credentials, and 
experience..

If you have any hesitation about providing personal 
information to us and/or having such information displayed 
on the Site or otherwise used in any manner permitted in 
this Privacy Policy and the applicable terms of service 
(the “Terms”), do not register or provide such information. 
Except as noted in this Privacy Policy, you do not need to 
be a registered user (a “User”) to access public portions of 
the Site, but your use of the Site and Services is conditioned 
on this Privacy Policy in any case.</string>
